==Offseason== *April 20, 2009: The University of Wyoming Cowgirl announced one addition to this year's recruiting class with the signing of Rebecca Campigli to attend the University of Wyoming beginning in the fall of 2009.<ref>http://www.wyomingathletics.com/sports/w-baskbl/spec-rel/042009aaa.html</ref>
